SUMMARY:smART Ventures Draft Review Session
DTSTAMP:20260326T123306Z
DTSTART:20260326T193000Z
DESCRIPTION:Event Types: Arts\,Training-Classes/Workshops\n\nNeighborhoo ds
	: Citywide\,Online Event\n\nContact: smART Ventures Team\n\nContact Email:
	 smartventures@seattle.gov\n\nAudience: All\n\nPre-Register: Yes\n\nCost: 
	Free\n\nLink: https://www.seattle.gov/arts/programs/grants/smart-ventures-
	grant\n\nMust attend a smART Ventures info session first\n\nAttend this gr
	oup session and bring 2-3 questions you may have regarding your applicatio
	n to share.\n\nSessions are available the 1st and 3rd Fridays of each mont
