BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:9p2EfIM65g9zabld3SQDv
SUMMARY:Robin Hood: ASL Interpreted Performance
DTSTAMP:20260326T123307Z
DTSTART:20260404T190000Z
DESCRIPTION:A wannabe king\, lawless law enforcement\, and the rich hoardin
	g all the wealth—it’s dark times in Nottingham. But out of the mists of ne
	arby Sherwood Forest comes the hero we’ve been waiting for.\n\nhttps://www
