	as she drugged during the meal? How did she end up in a hotel room after m
	eeting him in a restaurant? And if she was drugged\, is that why\, when sh
	e returns home\, her husband appears as fully alive and functioning and he
	adless?\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/wife-of-headless-
	man-investigates-her-own-disappearance/18216693/2026-04-06T00\n\nFrom SEAt
